要求
composer &gt;=1.0.0 (includes dev-master)
PHP &gt;=5.3, (suggest &gt;=5.5, because curl_share_init)
ext-curl
安装
$ composer global require hirak/prestissimo
卸载
$ composer global remove hirak/prestissimo
基准测试效果
288s -&gt; 26s</p>

